ng against this phenomenon. She analyses the proliferation of photo-forms-remediations of well-known photographs of troubling historical events rendered in such media as paint, celluloid, fabric, digital imagery, and tattoos-as imaginative spaces in which the shadows of secrecy are provocatively outlined.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 0aAltered printsxPolitical aspectszChina. 0aCollective memoryxPolitical aspectszChina. 0aNanking Massacre, Nanjing, Jiangsu Sheng, China, 1937. 0aOfficial secretsxSocial aspectszChina. 0aPhotographyxPolitical aspectszChinaxHistoryy20th century. 0aPhotography, HandworkedxPolitical aspectszChina. 0aPropaganda, Chinese. 7aHISTORY / Asia / China.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDUP Frontlist eBook-Package 2020z978311069631808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020 Englishz978311070473008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020z9783110704525oZDB-23-DEG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781478009047zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781478009047423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781478009047.jpg  a978-3-11-069631-8  DUP Frontlist eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-070471-6  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-070473-0  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2020 Englishb2020  aEBA_DUK_ALL  aEBA_DUK_EALL  aEBA_DUK_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DEGb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2020